{"type": "article", "id": 8604, "title": "LaYours 废报纸凳子", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-17T07:26:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235201ac1Y8vjK2zfZ9gCT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t废物利用是当代设计上的一个大趋势，设计师 Wenchuman 最近利用废旧的报纸设计了一款凳子。这款名为 LaYours 的凳子采用不锈钢凳子腿儿的结构基础，你只需要把家里面的废旧报纸，杂志，册子等铺在上面固定好，就可以做出你心仪的凳子，既废物利用，又充满了个性。Wenchuman 是一个特别有趣的设计师，他的“Endless”等作品都值得一看，这是<a href=\"http://wenchuman.com/blog/\" target=\"_blank\">他的个人主页</a>，感兴趣可以去看看。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052351574swkzKmVijGNWCRP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.3625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235158GeydWzlPivn681Kf.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235158nb1lJcKaHjLYSdRM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64238411\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235158rEJPjW9LN4F2eld3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.52083333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235159Xie9c38mRgoUSqxv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523520067QVUbs4rLTAqE9F.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}